OL,3,CNadhim Zahawi to stand down at next
OL,4,Cgeneral election
OL,6,FNadhim Zahawi, the MP for , has
OL,7,Fannounced he won't be standing in the
OL,8,Fnext general election.
OL,10,FThe former chancellor, who has been
OL,11,Fthe MP for the area for 14 years,
OL,12,Fposted a statement on social media
OL,13,Fsite X this morning, May 9.
OL,15,FIn the statement Mr Zahawi said: "With
OL,16,Fthe exception of convincing my wife to
OL,17,Fmarry me, it has been the greatest
OL,18,Fhonour of my life to represent the
OL,19,Fpeople of Stratford-on-Avon and serve
OL,20,Fas a Minister of the Crown.
