OL,6,FHe paid tribute to the people of
OL,7,FStratford-on-Avon, a constituency he
OL,8,Fhas served since 2010.
OL,10,FHe said was proud they could confide
OL,11,Fin him, adding: "Whether they are
OL,12,Fstruggling against the dead hand of
OL,13,Fbureaucracy, or are stricken by
OL,14,Ftragedy, being able to help them in
OL,15,Ftheir time of need remains one of the
OL,16,Fmost meaningful things I have ever
OL,17,Fdone".
