OL,6,FMr Zahawi was appointed as the health
OL,7,Fminister responsible for the
OL,8,Fdeployment of vaccines in November
OL,9,F2020, helping to lead the roll-out of
OL,10,Fvaccinations across the country.
OL,12,FHe was education secretary from
OL,13,FSeptember 2021 to July 2022 and had a
OL,14,Fshort stint as chancellor of the
OL,15,Fexchequer between July and September
OL,16,F2022.
