OL,6,FIn 2023, Rishi Sunak sacked Mr Zahawi
OL,7,Fas Tory Party chairman after an ethics
OL,8,Finquiry found he had broken the
OL,9,FMinisterial Code several times over
OL,10,Fhis tax affairs.
OL,12,FMr Sunak had ordered an investigation
OL,13,Finto him by Sir Laurie Magnus, his
OL,14,Findependent adviser on ministers'
OL,15,Finterests, following reports that the
OL,16,FTory chairman had paid a penalty as
OL,17,Fpart of an estimated #4.8 million
OL,18,Fsettlement dispute with HMRC.
