OL,6,FIn January 2024, Mr Zahawi made a
OL,7,Fcameo in ITV drama "Mr Bates vs The
OL,8,FPost Office", playing himself
OL,9,Fquestioning then- chief executive
OL,10,FPaula Vennells.
OL,12,FHe later said he believes the Post
OL,13,FOffice has a "case to answer for
OL,14,Fcorporate manslaughter" and "criminal
OL,15,Fwrongdoing".
OL,17,FMr Zahawi is the 65th Tory MP ` out of
OL,18,Fa total of 344 Conservatives in the
OL,19,FCommons ` to have announced they will
OL,20,Fnot stand at the next election.
